                        Guitar 2  -     Rhy. Fig. 3 six times, Rhy. Fig. 4b once


[tab]        Bridge  (guitars 1 & 2 tacet)
 The violin 1 part I got from the music book that was put out.  I figured out the rest of it and
arranged it for  guitar.  The 'other' section is just 'D' and 'C' chords being played. I don't
know what intrument(s) it is so that's why it's called 'other'.
